{"tid":1383402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[7.31上庭] 追究警察濫用暴力第一案","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T14:14:49.000Z","uid":263731,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"a4f74680d04e5719ae2e901804583badfa4195a5","tid":1383402,"uid":263731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:31:58.000Z","msg":"小弟早前搞左個「齊齊向盧偉聰追數」既event：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/2122780331182256/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2122780331182256%2F&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=70015c15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/2122780331182256/</a><br />\n<br />\n而家向大家報告返：除左我之外仲有另一位市民就6.12警察濫暴既事情向警務處處長盧偉聰提出小額索償，於是案件由7月30日改左7月31日早上9點開審，會先處理兩單案係唔係一併聆訊既問題。<br />\n<br />\n6.12當日已經覺得警察亂放催淚彈橡膠彈布袋彈好離譜。事隔個半月，警察濫暴既場面越來越多，越來越過份。而家睇返當日既片段已經開始覺得麻木。<br />\n<br />\n反送中運動去到今日情勢同6.12已經好唔同，初衷之一係守護法治，始終不變。不容許政權胡亂使用權力、濫用暴力，正正係法治既根本價值。所有警察濫用暴力既事件，我地唔應該慣、唔可以慣，一定要追究到底。<br />\n<br />\n7月31日9點鐘，西九龍法院第3法庭見。"},{"pid":"9b6b61af9c2166d09c5adea62a1ce6ca30018af0","tid":1383402,"uid":275074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:33:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2620622657bc7dbb9b30909a2ef44fbc21de35a","tid":1383402,"uid":117005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:34:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a11cbebe3a812ec79afc8f5b36d17b591e59fc8f","tid":1383402,"uid":291354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4f74680d04e5719ae2e901804583badfa4195a5","tid":1383402,"uid":263731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:31:58.000Z","msg":"小弟早前搞左個「齊齊向盧偉聰追數」既event：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/2122780331182256/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2122780331182256%2F&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=70015c15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.c